results.deck: Panasonic is an electronics manufacturer founded in 1918.
results.description: On October 4, 2010, Panasonic unveiled their new handheld named 'Jungle'. Jungle will be focused on online gaming & MMOs and will be able to run browser based games. The device is being cross promoted with the browser based MMO, Battlestar Galactica Online.
